comment: After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court that the ball was last touched by Hayward (UTA) was overturned and Utah was awarded possession.
Gasol (MEM) grabs Gobert's (UTA) arm and affects his ability to secure the rebound.
Green (MEM) does not affect Hood's (UTA) RSBQ at the start of his drive.
Green (MEM) maintains legal guarding position while defending the play to the basket by Hood (UTA).
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court that the ball was last touched by Exum (UTA) was upheld and Memphis retained possession.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the clock was adjusted to 0:01.2 to reflect the time the ball was knocked OOB by Memphis.

Gasol (MEM) cleanly blocks Hayward's (UTA) jump shot. There is contact after the blocked shot, but because the shot is already blocked, the contact to the hand is incidental and deemed to have no impact on the shot attempt.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court that Hayward (UTA) was fouled while attempting a 3 pointer prior to the game clock expiring was upheld.
